    "Name": "Kestrel",
    "Details": "The Kestrel is a close-combat specialist, combining the Phoenix Hawk’s top speed with 8 Improved Jump Jets for exceptional maneuverability and jumps up to 240 meters. Faulkner uses its battle claws to attack weak or damaged rear armor, famously ripping an opponent’s head off during a match. For ranged combat, it features two Medium Variable Speed Pulse Lasers linked to an advanced Targeting Computer, allowing precise, adjustable firepower. Ten double heat sinks cool the mech, though intense jumping and firing can strain them. The reliable 270 Standard engine and light armor balance cost with survivability, enabling it to keep fighting when others fall.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Aerial Assault</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
