  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Kestrel began as a worn-out Phoenix Hawk salvaged by dispossessed 'MechWarrior Steven Faulkner for Solaris VII arena combat. With no funds to restore it, a wealthy fan, Gerald Nezmith, stepped in to finance the rebuild. Nezmith customized the 'Mech to suit Faulkner's fighting style, including a battle claw and gimbal-mounted vector-thrust jump jets. Though heavily modified, the Kestrel retains the core of a PHX-1D, reimagined into a flashy and deadly performer in the arena circuit.",
